msgid ""
"**`wander`:** Random goal generation after reaching current goal (default: "
"`False`)"
msgstr "**`wander`：** 抵达当前目标后是否随机生成下一个目标（默认 `False`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:92
