"**`target_roles`:** Filter objects for behavior (`'all'`, `'robot'`, "
"`'obstacle'`)"
msgstr "**`target_roles`：** 行为作用对象筛选（`'all'`、`'robot'`、`'obstacle'`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:95
msgid "**RVO-specific Parameters:**"
msgstr "**RVO 专用参数：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:96
msgid ""
"**`vxmax`/`vymax`:** Maximum velocities in x/y directions (default: `1.5`)"
msgstr "**`vxmax`/`vymax`：** x/y 方向最大速度（默认 `1.5`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:97
msgid "**`acce`:** Maximum acceleration (default: `1.0`)"
msgstr "**`acce`：** 最大加速度（默认 `1.0`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:98
msgid ""
"**`factor`:** Collision penalty weight (default: `1.0`, higher = more "
"conservative)"
msgstr "**`factor`：** 碰撞惩罚权重（默认 `1.0`，越大越保守）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:99
msgid "**`mode`:** Algorithm variant - `'rvo'` (default), `'hrvo'`, or `'vo'`"
msgstr "**`mode`：** 算法模式——`'rvo'`（默认）、`'hrvo'` 或 `'vo'`"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:100
msgid ""
"**`neighbor_threshold`:** Detection range for nearby objects (default: `3.0`"
" meters)"
msgstr "**`neighbor_threshold`：** 邻近目标检测范围（默认 `3.0` 米）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:102
msgid ""
"**SFM-specific Parameters** (anisotropic Moussaid-Helbing 2009 variant):"
msgstr "**SFM 专用参数**（各向异性的 Moussaid-Helbing 2009 变体）："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:103
msgid "**`vmax`:** Speed cap applied after force integration (default: `1.5`)"
msgstr "**`vmax`：** 力积分后施加的速度上限（默认 `1.5`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:104
msgid ""
"**`neighbor_threshold`:** Social-interaction cutoff distance (default: "
"`10.0`)"
msgstr "**`neighbor_threshold`：** 社会力交互的距离截断（默认 `10.0`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:105
msgid "**`relaxation_time`:** Goal-pull time constant `tau` (default: `0.5`)"
msgstr "**`relaxation_time`：** 目标牵引时间常数 `tau`（默认 `0.5`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:106
msgid ""
"**`force_factor_desired`:** Weight on the goal-seeking force (default: "
"`1.0`)"
msgstr "**`force_factor_desired`：** 目标牵引力权重（默认 `1.0`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:107
msgid ""
"**`force_factor_social`:** Weight on inter-agent repulsion (default: `2.1`)"
msgstr "**`force_factor_social`：** 智能体间互斥力权重（默认 `2.1`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:108
msgid ""
"**`force_factor_obstacle`:** Weight on obstacle repulsion (default: `10.0`)"
msgstr "**`force_factor_obstacle`：** 障碍物互斥力权重（默认 `10.0`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:109
msgid ""
"**`sigma_obstacle`:** Exponential decay length of obstacle force (default: "
"`0.8`)"
msgstr "**`sigma_obstacle`：** 障碍物力的指数衰减长度（默认 `0.8`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:110
msgid ""
"**`lambda_importance`:** Relative weight of velocity vs. position in the "
"interaction direction (default: `2.0`)"
msgstr "**`lambda_importance`：** 在交互方向上速度相对位置的权重（默认 `2.0`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:111
msgid ""
"**`gamma`:** Sets the interaction range `B = gamma * ||t||` (default: "
"`0.35`)"
msgstr "**`gamma`：** 决定交互范围 `B = gamma * ||t||`（默认 `0.35`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:112
msgid ""
"**`n_angular`/`n_velocity`:** Angular sharpness exponents for the sideways "
"and slowdown components (defaults: `2.0`, `3.0`)"
msgstr "**`n_angular`/`n_velocity`：** 侧向力与减速力的角度锐度指数（默认分别为 `2.0`、`3.0`）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:114
msgid "**Dash-specific Parameters:**"
msgstr "**Dash 专用参数：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:115
msgid ""
