#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:444
msgid ""
"Use `group_behavior` in YAML for most cases as it handles initialization "
"automatically. For full control — custom collision logic or an external "
"planner — drive each robot yourself by passing velocity commands to "
"`env.step(action)` instead of setting a behavior."
msgstr ""
"大多数情况下在 YAML 中使用 `group_behavior`，它会自动处理初始化。若需要完全的控制 —— 自定义碰撞逻辑或外部规划器 —— "
"则不要设置 behavior，而是通过向 `env.step(action)` 传入速度指令来自行驱动每个机器人。"

