msgstr "下方给出了运行自定义行为所需的 Python 脚本与 YAML。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:752
msgid ""
"`load_behavior` function loads the custom behavior methods from the python "
"script. `custom_behavior_methods` is the name of the python script that "
"contains the custom behavior function."
msgstr ""
"`load_behavior` 函数会从 Python 脚本中加载自定义行为方法。`custom_behavior_methods` "
"是包含自定义行为函数的脚本名称。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_behavior.md:755
msgid ""
"Please place the script with the name `custom_behavior_methods` in the same "
"directory as the main python script."
msgstr "请将名为 `custom_behavior_methods` 的脚本与主 Python 脚本放在同一目录下。"

